         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botanic Garden ¶ 27/1/64 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you, that the printing of the second volume of the Universal work on Australian plants will commence in the month of march next...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">64.01.27b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">E64/974, unit 24, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne botanic Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">27/1/64</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you, that the printing of the second volume of the Universal work on Australian plants will commence in the month of march next and I would consequently solicit, that the sum of £100.- .-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which is as a subsidy available for this publication may be transmitted to the Agent General of Victoria at London and be thus rendered available to G. Bentham Esq, the President of the Linnean Society.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham (1863-78),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>2,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was issued<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>3 October 1864 (TL2). M had believed that the sum<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>previously<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>been<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>transmitted but<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>found on enquiry that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>it<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had not been (M to G. Bentham, 25 January 1864).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Approval for M's request was minuted to this letter.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient &amp; humble servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>&amp; <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>&amp;</p>
         </div>
      </body>
